item.description:
Join us for dinner and drinks at the Met Bar & Grill inside the Natick Collection as we celebrate the end of 2008 and the start of a great new year (a day early)! We will have dinner and then head back to the bar for after dinner drinks. Come relax and have a good time with friendly and interesting people. Everyone pays for their own food/drink.

The Met Bar & Grill serves classic American fare including a wide range of hamburgers, steaks, seafood and sandwiches.

Look forward to seeing you there!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) near bar. If necessary, please call 774 232 0000
